{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:16:33.085506+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "This repository is a **Spring Boot Java template** designed for early-stage projects where initial development productivity is prioritized. The README explicitly states: *\"This is not the best structure. This is a good basic structure to use early in the project when productivity is important. Remember, as your software grows, your structure must grow too.\"*\n\n## Module Structure\n\nThe project is organized into five top-level module groups, each containing one or more submodules:\n\n### 1. **Core** (Domain & Application Logic)\nThe core business modules, responsible for the main application:\n\n- **`core:core-api`**  \n  - The **only executable module** in the project (has `bootJar.enabled = true`).  \n  - Contains domain services, REST APIs, and framework configurations.  \n  - Structured to maximize initial development productivity by grouping all domains in one place.\n\n- **`core:core-enum`**  \n  - Contains enums shared across the application.  \n  - Acts as a lightweight dependency for external modules that need the enum definitions.\n\n### 2. **Clients** (External System Integration)\nModules for integrating with external systems via HTTP/API calls:\n\n- **`clients:client-example`**  \n  - Demonstrates HTTP communication using **Spring Cloud OpenFeign**.  \n  - Serves as a template for adding additional client integrations.\n\n### 3. **Storage** (Data Persistence)\nModules for data storage and access:\n\n- **`storage:db-core`**  \n  - Shows how to connect to **MySQL** using **Spring Data JPA**.  \n  - Provides the foundation for database access and repository patterns.\n\n### 4. **Support** (Cross-Cutting Concerns)\nModules for operational support and monitoring:\n\n- **`support:logging`**  \n  - Configures logging with support for **distributed tracing**.  \n  - Includes dependencies for **Sentry** error tracking.\n\n- **`support:monitoring`**  \n  - Provides service monitoring capabilities (likely Spring Boot Actuator and related tools).\n\n### 5. **Tests** (Test Infrastructure)\nModules for testing convenience and documentation:\n\n- **`tests:api-docs`**  \n  - Facilitates writing **Spring REST Docs** tests to generate API documentation.  \n  - Works with the `restDocsTest` task to produce AsciiDoc documentation.\n\n## Key Architectural Principles\n\n1. **Modular Growth**: The structure is designed to scale — each domain can eventually become its own submodule under `core`.\n2. **Separation of Concerns**: Clear boundaries between business logic (`core`), external integrations (`clients`), data persistence (`storage`), and operational concerns (`support`).\n3. **Standardized Testing**: Four test suites (`unitTest`, `contextTest`, `restDocsTest`, `developTest`) provide different testing scenarios.\n4. **Profile-Based Configuration**: Five runtime profiles (`local`, `local-dev`, `dev`, `staging`, `live`) support different environments.\n\n## Configuration Highlights\n\n- **Spring Boot 4.0.0** with **Spring Cloud 2025.1.0**\n- **Java 25** toolchain\n- All dependency versions managed centrally via `gradle.properties`\n- **Spring Java Format** enforced with pre-commit git hooks\n\nThis template provides a clean starting point for Spring Boot applications, with clear extension points for growing the system as business requirements evolve.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 1174, "prompt_tokens": 11321, "total_tokens": 12495, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 467, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 11072, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0011695542, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001481742, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00102138}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780863371-1LP5WEVXoGMiiTqtBoZV", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3ba-888a-7b32-b19e-1f08a73180e5-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11321, "output_tokens": 1174, "total_tokens": 12495, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 11072}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 467}}}}]}}}
